**Linux**
tar -zcvf target.tar.gz sourcefile
tar -zxvf target.tar.gz
du -hs pathMb
cp -r xx yy
wget http://a.com/b.jpg -P pic/wget
chmod 755 imgcatimgcatimgcat.sh , ./imgcat (sh imgcat.sh)
scp -r username@servername:/path/filename /target/path(-r )
sed 's/\t/,/g data.txtdata.txttab=>','
grep -o 'xxx' data.txt | wc -l
grep -r 'name' ./
data.txtxxx
name
iconv -f 'utf-8' -t 'gbk' a.txt > b.txtutf8=>gbk
sed -n '5,10p' data.txt
sed -n '10p' data.txt
cat nohup.out| head -n 100
cat nohup.out| tail -n 100 		5-1010,100100
hadoophadoop fs -getmerge /app/2016 data.txt2016mergedata.txt
hadoophadoop fs -cat,-lsfs
ps -ax
crontab -e
date +%Y-%m-%d
date -d yesterday +%Y%m%d
date -d tomorrow +%Y%m%d
date -d '30 days ago' +%Y%m%d
